{
  "stem": "3380.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were catching fish, you know, instead going to-- to-- to school, to go to Hebrew-- I mean, classes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kids are kids wherever you go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I grew up, I have seen there was no future in Poland for Jewish people and for the young-- youth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We will have to run away if the occasion-- I mean, if you're going to have a chance of running.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, for instance, people in France used to live a lot nicer and better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Germany, before Hitler came to power, people used to live more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had more freedom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism was not in Germany as embedded like it was by-- in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, in Germany, the anti-Semitism had to be brought out by Hitler.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Poland, there were no need for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember, in 1933, I was about 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to read the Jewish paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was very interested in what goes on in the world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe we have seen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all-- we didn't discuss.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we had discussions about it, but we know the end result will not-- probably will not be a good one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because, you see, even if the war wouldn't break out, that anti-Semitism, what's happened in Germany, reflect the countries all the way around Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were-- one-- one of the brothers-- we were only, let's say, certain-- certain places, we were only 50 miles or 40 kilometers for-- you know, from-- from the German border.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew exactly what was going on through radio and through the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all have seen the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And none of us could do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, in 1939, September the 1st, the war did broke out.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
